00:42:24.260 --> 00:42:29.620
asset to the portfolio's volatility, right?

00:42:29.620 --> 00:42:36.179
But each of these three documents, unparameterized, parameterized, and the Shiny app, if you look

00:42:36.179 --> 00:42:42.979
at their setups, which I'll toggle down to right now, their setups are all exactly the

